description:
These hard wearing scissors will last forever and ever.
Not only do they look good lying around your home or office they are also great for cutting string, cardboard and flower stems! 

Give them as a gift to yourself or a friend....

name: Handwoven Indigo Throw / Wrap
description:
A seriously beautiful Indigo Ikat throw / wrap. 
Will look amazing on the end of the bed or on the couch! 
Hand woven in Cambodia and $ go towards rural women with disabilities. Fair trade and natural organic colour and fabric. 
Only one in this style and thickness.
Hand woven pieces are not perfect but this gives them a rustic handmade feel. 250cm long and 112cm wide.

name: Interior Styling Consultation
description:
One hour consultation – we come to your home or business, and discuss what your requirements and aspirations are for your chosen space/s. Take photos and measurements of the space and if children are involved we also ask for their input.  

We are qualified Interior Designers that can assist in a large range of tasks. Including: Space planning, Storage suggestions, Paint colour choice, Furniture, Lighting and textiles. We can also help suggest ways of selling old furniture and how to style on a budget.

Each one is made of wood and covered in fine gold glitter. They look fantastic as a centre piece, on a lolly bar or any where in your home. Other words available. Friends, Family, Dreams, Believe, Hope, Hello. Others available too. Any questions please email interiorhunter@hotmail.com

name: Interior Styling Consultation: Events
description:
I can meet with you in person or i can assist you online. 
Lets discuss your wedding, hens, party or event. Lets chat about your ideas and let me see how i can assist you. Interior Stylist's can help bring all your ideas together and make your event look spectacular. We help you to express your style and we love to share our knowledge with you. We make planning an event less stressful and can save you money and time. We have suppliers, wholesalers and discounts we share with you. We make the process fun and most of all your event will be one to remember for all the right reasons...Email interiorhunter@hotmail.com to book an Interior Styling Consultation for your event.

name: Handwoven Throw
description: These handwoven fair trade throws are made in rural Cambodia and support women with disabilities. They are soft to touch and look great at the end of the bed or thrown over the couch. Also wonderful for a wedding gift or used as a babies blanket. 195cm x115cm. Some come with tassels and others with crotched edges. Please email interiorhunter@hotmail.com for colours. At least 10 different colours to choose from.

name: Life is beautiful jar with cork lid.
description:
This jar is made from strong durable glass and has a cork lid. The ceramic round tag with paisley block print has been hand made by us. The quote Life is beautiful will cheer you up any day! This can be used to store anything in and placed in your office, kitchen or bathroom. 
There is only one of this item and will not last long.

name: A bohemian friendship wristband is grand
description: These handcrafted wristbands can also be worn as an anklet too. They are made in india by rural tribal woman. Intricate stitching and inlayed mirrors make these a beautiful unique present for a friend. Includes free shipping.

name: Bohemian gypsy necklace
description: This special necklace has been handcrafted in rural India. It has shell detail and beautiful bright colours. A truly beautiful one of a kind piece that you can add to your collection. This piece could also be used as a wall hanging, framed or sewn onto a bag or dress.

name: Indian neck piece textile patch
description: This intricately stitched textile could be framed or sewed onto a dress. The silver metallic stitching has been hand sewed by rural woman in india. Little mirror inserts and extra colourful stitching completes this incredible one of a kind embroidery. Add this to your collection of special pieces or give it to someone that appreciates the detail and time it takes to make a unique piece like this.

name: Holy cow wall hanging is outstanding
description: This holy cow is very unique and special. It is hand painted and carved out of wood and paper mache in a remote part of India. It is said to ward off evil spirits from the family home and bring good luck if placed near the front entrance. Also would look great in a child's room or play room. A quirky new twist compared to the old deer on the wall. This holy cow will bring character to your happy home. Has a rustic feel and comes with markings ect for that old vintage look. Also has hardware on back for easy hanging. Includes free shipping.

name: Hardwood plate with ceramic insert.
description:
This recycled hardwood plate with vintage recycled ceramic insert is hand crafted in Cambodia and fair trade. 

Size: 18cm diameter and 3.5 thick.

Some of the profits go towards people with disabilities in rural Cambodia. 

The ceramic insert is made from the broken bowls that are used to give offerings to monks, so each insert is slightly different. All are hand painted in blue and all patterns are different. So you could say these plates have been blessed. 

The good quality recycled hardwood has been treated and is safe to eat off. These plates are perfect for serving your favourite sweets or starters on. 

Please email me for images if you would like to choose the pattern of the insert at interiorhunter@hotmail.com

name: Organic recycled natural cotton dish clothes
description: 100% recycled cotton natural dish cloths are unbleached. They look nice and last forever. x3 in a pack. Machine washable. Free Postage included.

name: Ganesh Indian ring good luck it will bring
description: This special Ganesh ring found in a busy market place in India is a perfect design for anyone. Ganesh is the remover of obstacles so who wouldn't want this popular deity heading out for the day with them. Perfect unisex flat design ring. Includes free shipping.

name: Happy Rain Cloud Nursery Art
description: This felt happy rain cloud art work is handcrafted and and has stitch detail. Looks fantastic above a change detail to add colour and simple shapes to a nursery or child's room. Can be custom made in any colour and includes free shipping.
